/*
1. use form tag and name to get values.
2. From e access e.target.[name of the input field].value and name to get values.
3. use individual field state.
4. controlled element: use individual field state for each input field
5. controlled element: one object in a state holding all the input fields value.
6. uncontroled element: useRef to create a reference to the element and access value by using like: nameRef.current.value

*/